<li class='cover' id='bookCover_673252'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/673252.Anne_McCaffrey_s_Dragonflight_1"><img alt="Anne McCaffrey&#39;s Dragonflight #1" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1202781748l/673252._SX98_.jpg" />
